1
00:00:00,511 --> 00:00:08,611
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,786 --> 00:00:17,023
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,262 --> 00:00:19,253
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,267 --> 00:00:26,033
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,104 --> 00:00:29,471
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,674 --> 00:00:33,235
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,611 --> 00:00:36,978
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,048 --> 00:00:44,477
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,555 --> 00:00:53,691
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,765 --> 00:01:01,797
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:08,878
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,947 --> 00:01:17,013
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,322 --> 00:01:25,787
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,863 --> 00:01:27,888
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:40,606 --> 00:01:47,011
<i>Sasuke's Decision.</i>
<i>Pushed to the Edge!</i>

16
00:02:00,926 --> 00:02:02,223
There you are!

17
00:02:09,601 --> 00:02:10,226
I'm here!

18
00:02:35,227 --> 00:02:36,251
I'm returning them to you!

19
00:02:45,237 --> 00:02:46,670
So it's a clone...

20
00:02:52,711 --> 00:02:53,507
Bastard!

21
00:02:58,317 --> 00:03:01,480
Sasuke... Uchiha...!

22
00:03:02,187 --> 00:03:04,451
Why won't you come at me?!

23
00:03:14,666 --> 00:03:15,826
Why...

24
00:03:16,969 --> 00:03:18,596
do you flee?!

25
00:03:20,472 --> 00:03:21,962
Ready?

26
00:03:22,174 --> 00:03:23,300
Over here!

27
00:03:27,045 --> 00:03:28,205
Over here!

28
00:03:28,714 --> 00:03:29,612
Wait!

29
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:32,912
Pass!

30
00:03:34,253 --> 00:03:35,686
Here! Good one!

31
00:03:36,421 --> 00:03:38,321
Good! Go! Go! Go!

32
00:03:45,964 --> 00:03:46,828
Power shot!

33
00:03:53,705 --> 00:03:54,899
What're we gonna do?

34
00:03:56,241 --> 00:03:59,233
We don't know any wall-climbing
techniques or anything...

35
00:04:10,289 --> 00:04:11,654
Y-You're...

36
00:04:19,765 --> 00:04:20,459
This...

37
00:04:20,666 --> 00:04:21,826
It's Gaara...

38
00:04:22,334 --> 00:04:23,801
Gaara of Sand...

39
00:04:24,436 --> 00:04:25,835
R-Run!

40
00:04:33,445 --> 00:04:34,207
Wait!

41
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,977
Don't leave me alone!

42
00:04:38,483 --> 00:04:39,882
Help me!

43
00:04:43,021 --> 00:04:43,680
<i>I don't...</i>

44
00:04:46,358 --> 00:04:47,689
<i>want to be alone anymore!</i>

45
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,030
<i>Really...</i>

46
00:04:57,469 --> 00:04:58,663
No!

47
00:05:04,776 --> 00:05:06,801
Gaara! Please calm down!

48
00:05:08,613 --> 00:05:09,511
Yashamaru...

49
00:05:45,984 --> 00:05:47,815
No escape!

50
00:05:48,353 --> 00:05:53,120
I won't let you escape!
Sasuke Uchiha!

51
00:06:13,345 --> 00:06:16,508
<i>You've gotta be kidding!</i>
<i>What's with that outrageous strength...?</i>

52
00:06:17,582 --> 00:06:19,914
Are you afraid of me?

53
00:06:21,052 --> 00:06:22,485
<i>It's too overwhelming...</i>

54
00:06:23,688 --> 00:06:31,390
Sasuke Uchiha! Are you afraid?
Are you afraid of my existence?!

55
00:06:33,532 --> 00:06:37,992
<i>Don't forget...</i>
<i>You are my prey.</i>

56
00:06:40,906 --> 00:06:41,600
Wait!

57
00:06:44,976 --> 00:06:48,275
Why are you fixated
on me so much?

58
00:06:57,389 --> 00:07:00,017
Those eyes that know true loneliness...

59
00:07:03,128 --> 00:07:09,465
And eyes that know that
it is the world's greatest suffering...

60
00:07:10,335 --> 00:07:11,302
I think I told you.

61
00:07:12,304 --> 00:07:15,137
That you have the same eyes as me.

62
00:07:16,074 --> 00:07:17,564
Eyes that lust for power,

63
00:07:17,642 --> 00:07:20,907
overflowing with hatred
and murderous intent...

64
00:07:23,348 --> 00:07:24,872
The same as me...

65
00:07:26,051 --> 00:07:29,646
Eyes that burn to kill those
who drove you...

66
00:07:31,690 --> 00:07:34,284
into a hell called Ioneliness!

67
00:07:40,866 --> 00:07:41,924
Such are your eyes.

68
00:07:49,441 --> 00:07:50,601
Okay. Just a minute.

69
00:07:53,378 --> 00:07:54,902
So you're called Gaara...

70
00:07:57,082 --> 00:08:00,142
I don't know what you know
about Sasuke, but...

71
00:08:01,219 --> 00:08:02,846
It's not good for you to
speak as though

72
00:08:02,921 --> 00:08:04,889
you perceive everything about Sasuke!

73
00:08:06,124 --> 00:08:08,786
What is it that you want to say
to him before the final round,

74
00:08:08,894 --> 00:08:10,623
by pursuing him so far?

75
00:08:12,664 --> 00:08:14,154
A battle is where...

76
00:08:16,568 --> 00:08:19,196
another's existence and one's own
existence are put on the line...

77
00:08:21,172 --> 00:08:23,037
and each tries to kill the other!

78
00:08:25,777 --> 00:08:30,373
Only the winner can actually feel
the value of his own existence.

79
00:08:31,082 --> 00:08:32,777
In other words,
what you want to say is...

80
00:08:32,851 --> 00:08:36,218
let's have a killing bout and
not a match?

81
00:08:36,755 --> 00:08:41,624
Uchiha... You really should
be wanting it, too...

82
00:08:42,327 --> 00:08:44,158
in the depths of your soul...

83
00:08:44,963 --> 00:08:48,057
You want to confirm
the value of your existence.

84
00:08:48,567 --> 00:08:51,832
Am I really, truly powerful?

85
00:08:52,537 --> 00:08:55,301
Is my existence more powerful
than my opponent

86
00:08:55,373 --> 00:08:57,933
who faces me with eyes
filled with intent to kill?

87
00:09:17,362 --> 00:09:18,761
What's the matter?!

88
00:09:19,965 --> 00:09:21,865
Sasuke Uchiha!

89
00:09:22,534 --> 00:09:24,866
Are you afraid of me?!

90
00:09:28,607 --> 00:09:30,837
Your hatred and intent to kill...

91
00:09:31,476 --> 00:09:33,876
have they given way to fear?

92
00:09:34,446 --> 00:09:38,109
Is that the extent of your existence?!

93
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:42,377
Fight me... and confirm it!

94
00:09:43,388 --> 00:09:46,687
Your value! Your existence!

95
00:09:47,359 --> 00:09:48,758
Experience it!

96
00:09:49,561 --> 00:09:51,119
If you want an answer...

97
00:09:52,597 --> 00:09:53,689
Come at me!

98
00:10:04,809 --> 00:10:06,106
<i>I was allowed to live...</i>

99
00:10:07,746 --> 00:10:10,476
<i>Only...myself.</i>

100
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,012
<i>Expressly for what reason?!</i>

101
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:18,553
<i>No... I know the reason.</i>

102
00:10:19,724 --> 00:10:23,660
<i>The reason that man left me alive</i>
<i>was so he wouldn't be tormented</i>

103
00:10:23,728 --> 00:10:26,629
<i>by a sense of guilt for having killed</i>
<i>an entire clan...</i>

104
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:36,366
<i>Itachi chose me as the avenger...</i>
<i>in order to have me kill him!</i>

105
00:10:51,823 --> 00:10:56,658
Now, let me have some fun...
Sasuke Uchiha!

106
00:10:59,864 --> 00:11:01,297
I'll finish it with one blow!

107
00:11:43,542 --> 00:11:46,010
Hurry up and die,
release yourself from your misery.

108
00:11:46,845 --> 00:11:48,745
You silly old fool...

109
00:11:49,648 --> 00:11:53,414
I believe I told you...
that you would die too!

110
00:11:54,219 --> 00:11:55,151
Bastard!

111
00:12:03,261 --> 00:12:05,286
Let go, you old fool!

112
00:12:05,664 --> 00:12:08,792
I will not let go!
I <i>refuse</i> to let go...

113
00:12:09,034 --> 00:12:12,595
until I have pulled out your soul!

114
00:12:25,016 --> 00:12:26,540
<i>At this rate...</i>

115
00:12:59,451 --> 00:13:00,145
Gaara!

116
00:13:06,925 --> 00:13:08,392
<i>Looks like it worked...</i>

117
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:35,210
I see! That's what it was!

118
00:13:35,420 --> 00:13:36,387
That's not possible...

119
00:13:36,621 --> 00:13:40,387
He countered Gaara's attack
in that condition?!

120
00:13:45,564 --> 00:13:50,467
I just realized the reason...
why it's so fun!

121
00:13:52,103 --> 00:13:53,365
This pain...

122
00:13:54,472 --> 00:13:57,498
To take down an opponent
who wounded me...

123
00:13:57,709 --> 00:14:00,200
and thoroughly destroy him...!

124
00:14:00,345 --> 00:14:04,111
<i>That</i> will make me truly feel alive!

125
00:14:06,117 --> 00:14:10,850
<i>Gaara's never had a single wound,</i>
<i>but he got Gaara twice.</i>

126
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:14,923
<i>Is he...a freak?!</i>

127
00:14:15,961 --> 00:14:19,021
<i>No...a true freak is...</i>

128
00:14:20,966 --> 00:14:25,665
<i>After all, the only thing Gaara is</i>
<i>transforming is still just his right arm.</i>

129
00:14:30,575 --> 00:14:32,543
More, more!

130
00:14:32,978 --> 00:14:33,706
What?!

131
00:14:45,357 --> 00:14:47,222
<i>What the heck is this guy?!</i>

132
00:14:47,859 --> 00:14:49,383
<i>One after another...</i>

133
00:14:52,764 --> 00:14:55,289
<i>Here goes!</i>

134
00:14:57,068 --> 00:14:57,966
<i>He's even faster!</i>

135
00:15:09,948 --> 00:15:12,917
<i>I can't dodge unless</i>
<i>I read ahead of his movements.</i>

136
00:15:13,885 --> 00:15:16,217
<i>If I didn't have these eyes</i>
<i>I'd have died long ago.</i>

137
00:15:20,725 --> 00:15:21,851
<i>I can no longer use Chidori...</i>

138
00:15:22,994 --> 00:15:25,986
Fire Style...
Fire Ball Jutsu!

139
00:15:34,339 --> 00:15:35,863
<i>So the Fire Style doesn't</i>
<i>work against sand...</i>

140
00:15:36,508 --> 00:15:38,533
<i>Not only that,</i>
<i>this level of Jutsu won't...</i>

141
00:15:39,210 --> 00:15:40,700
Die!

142
00:15:41,379 --> 00:15:43,074
<i>Apparently...it needs to be Chidori!</i>

143
00:16:07,172 --> 00:16:11,700
Well! Your limit is two shots.
That's about it...

144
00:16:20,719 --> 00:16:23,244
This is as many Chidori
you can shoot in one day

145
00:16:23,321 --> 00:16:24,447
with your present Chakra.

146
00:16:25,557 --> 00:16:28,526
After all, this Chidori is a technique
that can only be used

147
00:16:28,593 --> 00:16:30,788
in conjunction with Sharingan
during actual battles.

148
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:36,462
But using Sharingan and
another Jutsu simultaneously means

149
00:16:36,868 --> 00:16:41,168
exploding and using up the Chakra
in your body all at once.

150
00:16:48,279 --> 00:16:51,806
Well! But you really are
one of the more impressive ones.

151
00:16:52,517 --> 00:16:53,779
Even with my Chidori...

152
00:16:54,152 --> 00:16:56,950
If I use the Lightning Blade
four times in a day,

153
00:16:57,388 --> 00:16:59,948
I'd completely use up my Chakra.

154
00:17:03,361 --> 00:17:06,922
What would happen if I tried
to use more than two shots?

155
00:17:10,902 --> 00:17:13,097
The third shot won't be activated...

156
00:17:14,038 --> 00:17:15,232
Remember this well!

157
00:17:16,775 --> 00:17:19,073
If you try to force a Jutsu to activate...

158
00:17:19,477 --> 00:17:21,741
not only will the Jutsu
not properly activate,

159
00:17:21,846 --> 00:17:23,711
but your Chakra will deplete to zero...

160
00:17:24,616 --> 00:17:26,675
And in the worst case, you'll die!

161
00:17:29,454 --> 00:17:34,357
Even if you were to survive,
absolutely nothing good will come of it.

162
00:17:36,427 --> 00:17:38,088
Especially in your case.

163
00:17:46,738 --> 00:17:47,898
What's the matter?

164
00:17:48,706 --> 00:17:51,903
Does the value of your existence
amount to only this much?

165
00:17:52,777 --> 00:17:54,267
I'll be blunt...

166
00:17:54,979 --> 00:17:57,641
You are... weak!

167
00:18:01,753 --> 00:18:04,017
You're too optimistic.

168
00:18:04,656 --> 00:18:06,954
And it's because your hatred
is weak!

169
00:18:09,561 --> 00:18:12,724
The power of hatred is
the power of the intent to kill!

170
00:18:13,665 --> 00:18:16,793
The power of the intent to kill
is the power of revenge!

171
00:18:23,074 --> 00:18:26,510
Your hatred is weaker than mine!

172
00:18:27,478 --> 00:18:28,240
Shut up...

173
00:18:30,715 --> 00:18:32,808
Do you understand
the meaning of this?!

174
00:18:33,651 --> 00:18:34,481
Shut up!

175
00:18:35,353 --> 00:18:40,017
That means that you...
You are weaker than me!

176
00:18:44,128 --> 00:18:50,192
<i>Itachi chose me to be the avenger...</i>
<i>to have me kill him!</i>

177
00:18:53,404 --> 00:18:54,962
<i>I am an avenger!</i>

178
00:20:11,249 --> 00:20:12,807
<i>The Curse Mark again...</i>

179
00:20:20,391 --> 00:20:22,552
<i>Darn...! My body...</i>

180
00:20:42,580 --> 00:20:43,444
Sasuke!

181
00:21:05,770 --> 00:21:15,839
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

182
00:21:16,281 --> 00:21:27,124
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

183
00:21:37,235 --> 00:21:42,867
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

184
00:21:42,941 --> 00:21:47,901
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

185
00:21:48,279 --> 00:21:53,182
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

186
00:21:53,251 --> 00:21:58,382
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

187
00:21:58,456 --> 00:22:08,627
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

188
00:22:08,933 --> 00:22:19,366
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

189
00:22:19,444 --> 00:22:30,013
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

190
00:22:30,088 --> 00:22:35,651
<i>Forge on strong</i>

191
00:22:47,539 --> 00:22:51,339
Hey Yashamaru,
what does pain feel like?

192
00:22:51,843 --> 00:22:54,641
I don't know because
I've never been injured...

193
00:22:54,979 --> 00:22:57,607
I was wondering what it's like.

194
00:22:58,516 --> 00:23:01,917
Could it be that I'm hurt?

195
00:23:02,554 --> 00:23:06,650
I'm not bleeding, but my chest's
felt weird for a long time.

196
00:23:07,125 --> 00:23:11,391
It feels stifled and it hurts a lot!

197
00:23:11,896 --> 00:23:14,194
Next time:
"Assassin of the Moonlit Night"
